name: A peak into tomorrow.
description:
We often feel like we'd live life better or maybe more or even less today, if only we could see what tomorrow held in store. Somehow we're always conscious of the fact that our actions today will yield results tomorrow and we often hope to know what the stakes are tomorrow so we could take the best actions today. 
This photo represents the opportunity to do that by asking you to trust your gut and have faith in yourself.
